OL,5, The closure of some petrol stations has
OL,6, reignited a row over lorry driver      
OL,7, shortages, which have disrupted supply 
OL,8, chains across the UK.                  
OL,10,FA "handful" of BP stations were closed 
OL,11,Fdue to a lack of available fuel, as    
OL,12,Fwell as a small number of Esso-owned   
OL,13,FTesco Alliance stations on Thursday.   
OL,15,FDriver shortages have been exacerbated 
OL,16,Fby the Covid-19 pandemic and Brexit.   
OL,18,FThe Road Haulage Association has urged 
OL,19,Fthe government to reconsider relaxing  
OL,20,Fvisa requirements for lorry drivers.   
